Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:05.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:08.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What miracle is going to happen \Nunder the moonlight tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh... So you know the owner, Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:23.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It looks like his name should be "Terai," \Nbut it's pronounced "Jii." Weird, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll call him Jii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, Saturday afternoon \Nand the place is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:36.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're good, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:45.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're really good, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jii-chan! Coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:52.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna serve myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:58.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:00.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that, getting me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I mean this coffee's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:06.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're worse than me, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not a hustler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:12.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:14.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give me "magician"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:16.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've never beaten me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:17.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:24.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You been yakkety-yakkin' since comin' in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:26.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Brats shouldn't be shootin' \Npool to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:31.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't have this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a place to hit balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not a place to hit people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want to hit somebody, do it elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:44.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You won't be givin' me \Nthe high hat much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This place is deserted with all your \Ncustomers flockin' to the boss's pool bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:50.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:54.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The boss has the Legendary Cue \Nat his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why nobody's comin' \Nto your hole in the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get lost, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:05.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The next time I come, it'll be to \Nbuy this place from you dirt cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:09.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:12.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But what was he saying \Nabout some "Legendary Cue"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:16.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Legendary Cue is inlaid with \Ncountless diamonds and emeralds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:21.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and it's said that only \Na champion can wield it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:24.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Diamonds and emeralds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:27.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know about the place that has that cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the pool hall called American \Nin front of the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:36.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hear you have to be 18 or over\N and dressed up to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Billiards should be fun to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:43.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Age and clothes have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:48.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, I'd like to get a look \Nat an awesome cue like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I used to own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you have it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:59.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I played a game of pool, \Nwith that cue as the stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:09.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Before I met your father, Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:48.26,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Hustler vs. Magician
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:05.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Back then, I used to rake \Nit in as a pool shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A pool shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, pool is an \Nenjoyable pastime for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:13.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but back in the day, it was \Nall about the gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:21.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I was a lone wolf who never lost, but \Nsome people didn't take kindly to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hasura Tsujiro worked for the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He was a sharp hustler \Nat the top of his game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We were tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I made just one error.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:52.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,From that point on, \NHasura had control of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and I never got another turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But you were an expert, right, Jii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How could you have blown it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:05.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unbeknownst even to Hasura,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:09.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the syndicate boss doctored my chalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You didn't object?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A showdown is a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice it then, and I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:21.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, Hasura really was talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've done a lot for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so I'll get that Legendary Cue back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tsujiro, come here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I got somethin' interesting to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}To Hasura-sama: \NI'm going to take \Nthe Legendary Cue \Nat 10:00 tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss, should we call the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:07.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot! They're already keeping \Nan eye on us these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ask them for even more attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:15.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Man, Aoko is always late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:23.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What kind of outfit is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You look like a middle school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Presto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...you gotta wear something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:42.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You touched my butt back there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You always have to act like a perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How else was I supposed to dress you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:55.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then you did touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you two really college students?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! We're married!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:09.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,P-Please come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:20.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Chocolate ice cream. Make it a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:27.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll know you're still a kid \Nif you order stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I like it! What can I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll have a chocolate parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:40.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How about ordering an adult-like cocktail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cocktail? With alcohol? Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Martini, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Skip the alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:03.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good grief. But maybe she at least \Nlooks like she belongs here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:10.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's that Hasura guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:15.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I believe Hasura-sama is \Nplaying in the secret room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Secret room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:22.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir, but there's a 50,000 yen charge \Njust for being a spectator in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Three... two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:31.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm with {\i1}Weekly Magic Sunday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:38.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and we want to publish an article in next \Nweek's issue, called "Just Like a Magician!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"The Cool Techniques of a Brilliant Hustler."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's for an article?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're leaving me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nine ball in the corner pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:15.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's definitely Tsujiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell? That was a lousy shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:33.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're gonna make the Legendary \NCue cry with skill like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jii, huh? He comes in here \Nafter all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We were just supposed to observe tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as I get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're from a magazine, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:50.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why don't you play against Tsujiro once?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'm game!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Jii.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tsujiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:01.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Which one should I go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jii, is he a hustler?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:07.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:11.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One game, 10,000 yen. \NLet's go with nine ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nine ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know straight pool, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:20.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master, you're at a disadvantage \Nif you don't know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:24.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Jii-chan! It's still just a \Nmatter of knocking the balls in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Except in straight ball, \Nyou can target any of the balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,whereas with nine ball, \Nyou have to sink them in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:38.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if you brilliantly knock in the \Neight ball, miss nine and you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:50.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you knock the nine ball in \Nduring the opening break, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Heck, it sounds easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:26.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You did know that sinking the cue ball
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is a foul?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm unlucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You certainly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hasura-sama is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:43.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...nine ball is a game of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And drawing the luck to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...is a type of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:02.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it! He doesn't only have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got guts that attract luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:11.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. This is a match \Nbetween an adult and a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna quit while you're behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Up yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tsujiro won this set, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:53.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's 100,000 in losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master, I can't afford...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:02.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's raise the stakes. We'll put the \NBlue Parrot pool hall on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And for your side, \Nyou put up the Legendary Cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:15.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Young Master! How am I supposed to \Nmake a living if I lose my place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! What's a business or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, that place
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is Kid the Phantom Thief's headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:30.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't play, knowing that I would \Ntake away Jii's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do it. We can make good money \Nwith that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:38.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Zip it. Your job is to hit \Nthe balls in like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:38.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not askin' you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's an order, Tsujiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He accepts the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:50.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm just a tool to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:57.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, a showdown is a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:03.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Jii, but I'm gonna win this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:08.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sink the one, then a two-nine \Ncombination to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Miss, I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito! I'm here to cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A nuisance got in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The balls are fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why are you playing this slow crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito can't win with music like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Um, something that Kaito likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, now we're talkin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:53.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Seems like Lady Luck's on my side now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He looks like he's having so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:14.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do I enjoy myself like that \Nduring matches these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Would you cut the noise when it's his turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't have him getting distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Billiards is a game you play for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And besides, as for his turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He ain't gonna get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:37.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't even sink the easy shots, so \Nthere's no way you can handle this setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that position...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Toichi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:56.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, who do you think is the \Nmost important person in a circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The person on the flying trapeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The clowns are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Clowns are lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:13.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, to satisfy the audience, \Nthey have to fail deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:17.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's even more difficult than succeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:23.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But clowns have to laugh the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:27.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's to catch the audience off guard \Nand heighten their amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's their poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:33.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The cue ball made two jumps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You did it, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're not gettin' that cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! You said you'd give it if I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As always, adults are liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And lying is the first step \Nto becoming a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After learning the secret, you have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:44.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hope you like the flavor \Nof my paralyzing powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito! You can't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:53.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As promised, I'm absconding \Nwith the Legendary Cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:56.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait! Your advance notice is nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:00.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your note said you were going \Nto steal the cue from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but now it belongs to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That cue can only belong to a true champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been protecting it for 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and now I want to give it to that \Nyoung man with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'm embarrassed for my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:23.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Acting outside the bounds of my advance notice \Nwould bring shame to my good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:27.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I shall take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're the Organized Crime Task Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nobody move! You're under \Narrest for gun smuggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will you come with us down \Nto the station voluntarily?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:50.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're very talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:53.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah. I was just lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? There are two Kaitos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:03.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems you can use magic \Nto manipulate luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:10.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But no matter what happens, \Na showdown is a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I lost this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:18.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But if you don't mind, I'd like to \Nplay against you again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where did Jii-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Young Master works \Nthis old man too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:42.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you were \Na hustler, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:47.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up. I told you that was just dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Boy, you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:52.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never beat me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You relied on luck with my business at stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the difference? I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at this shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:05.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm not a hustler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're on a lucky streak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The battle between a hustler and a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:36.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Was it luck or the poker face \Nof a clown that won the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:38.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:42.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm devoting myself to stealing as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:26.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,when an arrogant guy just back \Nfrom England appears before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:28.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Detectives are a phantom thief's rivals,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:33.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but I haven't met one yet \Nwho's a match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:37.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So, you wanna show me what you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:42.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NA Great Detective Comes to Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:42.73,Signs,,0,0,0,,A Great Detective Comes to Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:45.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:48.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
